name: Yodlee
description: Powered by the award-winning Yodlee platform, the Yodlee Interactive financial cloud is an innovation delivery system for entrepreneurs, partners, and developers to build the next generation of digital financial services, plus any service or process that can be created, improved, or enhanced by streamlined access to data, payments, and/or digital security.
